ZH: 我们需要密切关注项目的进度。
EN: We need to closely monitor the progress of the project.

ZH: 经理昨天检查了施工工地的进度。
EN: The manager checked the progress of the construction site yesterday.

ZH: 我们必须尽快加快工作进度。
EN: We must accelerate the pace of work as soon as possible.

ZH: 请确保按计划完成整个项目的进度。
EN: Please ensure that the progress of the entire project is completed as planned.

ZH: 项目的进度比预期快了两天。
EN: The project is progressing two days ahead of schedule.

ZH: 我们已经完成了任务的一半，进度还算不错。
EN: We have completed half of the task, and the progress is not bad.

ZH: 因为设备故障，工作进度受到了很大的影响。
EN: The progress of the work has been greatly affected due to equipment failure.

ZH: 请将最新的进度报告发送给我。
EN: Please send me the latest progress report.

ZH: 项目进度的延迟可能导致额外的成本。
EN: The delay in project progress may lead to additional costs.

ZH: 我们需要制定一份详细的进度计划。
EN: We need to develop a detailed schedule plan.

ZH: 请准确估计工作的进度所需的时间。
EN: Please accurately estimate the time required for the progress of the work.

ZH: 我们需要调整进度安排以适应客户的要求。
EN: We need to adjust the schedule to meet the requirements of the client.

ZH: 技术问题导致了工作进度的延误。
EN: Technical issues have caused a delay in the progress of the work.

ZH: 为了保持进度，我们需要增加人力资源。
EN: In order to maintain progress, we need to increase the manpower.

ZH: 请定期更新项目进度表。
EN: Please update the project progress chart regularly.

ZH: 进度的落后可能会对整个项目造成影响。
EN: The lag in progress may have an impact on the entire project.

ZH: 我们需要确保工作的进度逐步稳定增长。
EN: We need to ensure that the progress of the work steadily grows.

ZH: 项目进行得太快可能会导致质量问题。
EN: The project progressing too fast may lead to quality issues.

ZH: 我们需要密切跟踪工作进度，避免出现延误。
EN: We need to closely track the progress of the work to avoid delays.

ZH: 请将每天的进度报告发送给相关人员。
EN: Please send the daily progress report to the relevant personnel.
